'''Chris Sprouse''' is comic book artist best known for ''Tom Strong'' by [[Alan Moore]]. His work is included in [[Star Wars: Splinter of the Mind's Eye (comic series)|''Splinter of the Mind's Eye'']] comic, ''[[Star Wars: Luke Skywalker, Last Hope for the Galaxy]]''and [[Star Wars: Age of Rebellion (comic series)|''Star Wars: Age of Rebellion'']].

